"{\"uid\": \"click2houston.com-news-local-2024-04-17-100-days-to-the-2024-olympics-in-paris-full-countdown-and-dates-to-lookout-for\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Erica Young, News Producer  Published:April 17, 2024 at 4:40 AM  Updated:April 17, 2024 at 6:45 PM  Recommended Videos  Erica Young, News Producer  It's starting to get real.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 5, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erica_Kane\", \"score\": 0.99999292993969, \"rank\": 6.754986795421738e-06, \"text\": \"Erica\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erica_Kane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erica_Kane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have had a lot of signs this week that the 2024 Summer Olympics is getting closer.\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 261, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Team USA Media Summit was held this week in New York City, where KPRC 2\\u2032s Keith Garvin and Daniella Guzman got to interview some high-profile athletes.\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 266, \"end\": 274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9760609035705567, \"rank\": 0.024496556923508057, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999998844942, \"rank\": 1.0717058515523192e-10, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garvin\", \"score\": 0.9994981034028115, \"rank\": 0.0005021437279276517, \"text\": \"Garvin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\