uly 26  SOME OTHER KEY DATES TO MARK ON YOUR CALENDAR  Many athletes still have to compete in trials before even learning if they will qualify for the 2024 Games.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The swimming trials will be held June 15-23 in Indianapolis, Indiana.\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1287, \"end\": 1299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"score\": 0.9982495720446298, \"rank\": 0.0017513432673631197, \"text\": \"Indianapolis\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\"}, {\"begin\": 1301, \"end\": 1308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\", \"score\": 0.999986980276564, \"rank\": 6.278281040186116e-06, \"text\": \"Indiana\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The diving trials will be held June 16-23 in Knoxville, Tennessee.\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McGhee_Tyson_Airport\", \"score\": 0.9999958825376964, \"rank\": 4.115056982541499e-06, \"text\": \"Knoxville, Tennessee\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McGhee_Tyson_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McGhee_Tyson_Airport\"}, {\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McGhee_Tyson_Airport\", \"score\": 0.9999958825376964, \"rank\": 4.115056982541499e-06, \"text\": \"Knoxville, Tennessee\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McGhee_Tyson_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McGhee_Tyson_Airport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, The track and field trials will be held June 21-30 in Eugene, Oregon.\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1446, \"end\": 1452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"score\": 0.6010534547683675, \"rank\": 0.663393121173211, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally, the gymnastics trials will be held June 27-30 in Minneapolis, Minnesota.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1526, \"end\": 1535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.998746691514798, \"rank\": 0.0004995075514568753, \"text\": \"Minnesota\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"COMPETITION DATES FOR MOST POPULAR EVENTS  Gymnastics will take place between July 27 and August 5.\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1581, \"end\": 1591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999999556675913, \"rank\": 2.938347329328261e-08, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Track and field events will be held between August 1 and August 11.\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Followed by Swimming competitions from July 27 through August 4.\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1720, \"end\": 1728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9947738438417897, \"rank\": 0.004973519466226213, \"text\": \"Swimming\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the new Olympic sport